  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/299660/extras/f03956c352d1e51e010424d9ec1fe9dd.poster.avif?t=1758258062\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/299660/extras/f03956c352d1e51e010424d9ec1fe9dd.webm?t=1758258062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/299660/extras/f03956c352d1e51e010424d9ec1fe9dd.mp4?t=1758258062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/299660/extras/1bc32b6f1c7fadc6e9f6c2b49c9af941.poster.avif?t=1758258062\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/299660/extras/1bc32b6f1c7fadc6e9f6c2b49c9af941.webm?t=1758258062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/299660/extras/1bc32b6f1c7fadc6e9f6c2b49c9af941.mp4?t=1758258062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Let's super high jump through the screen!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6180 the moon is a platformer game with a unique mechanic. It offers a fresh, unseen game play style by connecting the top and bottom of the screen. This allows in a mechanic with delightfully long jumps and no fear of \"slipping\" to death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the unique gameplay, 6180 the moon delivers a unique storyline. The Sun has gone. The Moon sets off on a journey to find the Sun. Along the journey will be hazardous courses and deep realizations.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/299660/extras/f03956c352d1e51e010424d9ec1fe9dd.poster.avif?t=1758258062\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/299660/extras/f03956c352d1e51e010424d9ec1fe9dd.webm?t=1758258062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/299660/extras/f03956c352d1e51e010424d9ec1fe9dd.mp4?t=1758258062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/299660/extras/1bc32b6f1c7fadc6e9f6c2b49c9af941.poster.avif?t=1758258062\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/299660/extras/1bc32b6f1c7fadc6e9f6c2b49c9af941.webm?t=1758258062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/299660/extras/1bc32b6f1c7fadc6e9f6c2b49c9af941.mp4?t=1758258062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Let's super high jump through the screen!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6180 the moon is a platformer game with a unique mechanic. It offers a fresh, unseen game play style by connecting the top and bottom of the screen. This allows in a mechanic with delightfully long jumps and no fear of \"slipping\" to death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the unique gameplay, 6180 the moon delivers a unique storyline. The Sun has gone. The Moon sets off on a journey to find the Sun. Along the journey will be hazardous courses and deep realizations.</p>",
